Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道是這樣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不如保持冷淡還好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我便不會注意到自己喜歡哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會因為知道亞絲娜的事情而難過...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會為了取代哥哥而喜歡上桐人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要...管我了...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我變得不明白與家人之間的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這家裡真正的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道這一切是在我十歲時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人究竟是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我真的了解這個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種違和感...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是讓我進入網路遊戲發展的原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不認識真實的對方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛偽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我便開始沈溺於舒適的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在SAO的兩年裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變了我的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是現實世界還是假想世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本質其實都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要去相信並且接受別人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們所認識的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是他最真實的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到這個世界後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到小直臉的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真心感到非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要全力彌補這幾年來我和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小直之間產生的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能為小直所做的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在阿魯恩北邊的露臺上等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明說了那麼過分的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是堅強...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒辦法像你一樣堅強啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時 我還對他說了要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在卻在這裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 該說些什麽呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉法！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我找妳好久了 莉法！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷、雷根？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被火精靈抓住了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把他們全部毒殺 然後逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒殺...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我追著莉法來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個守衛精靈到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對那個人說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了些絕對不該說出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...真是個笨蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我說了些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再跟那個人見面了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回司伊魯班去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉法...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉法！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉法妳不能哭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什、什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉上沒有笑容就不是莉法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直待在妳身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是在真實世界還是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不會讓妳獨自一人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我、我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡莉法...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是喜歡直葉妳啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒、沒事吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要我鼓起勇氣告白就肯定會成功的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也得像你學習才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小直...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 來比試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天比試的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次可不會讓妳囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪那時會是那種姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要跟小直道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定要受妳一劍...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是該道歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在真正的意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒從那個世界裡回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一切還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她還沒醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在現實裡的生活就無法開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在還不知道該如何去考慮小直的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等哥哥能真正回到家裡來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究、究竟要做什麽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要攻略世界樹唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我總共三人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結衣妳在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才跟那些守衛的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有得到什麼情報嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些守衛騎士的能力值並不高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是出現的數量實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能說難易度是設定在無法攻略的等級之上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總體來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟絕對無敵的大魔王一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過憑著爸爸的技能熟練度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一瞬間的機會能突破重圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以陪我再冒一次險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會竭盡所能來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然這傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 因為我和莉法是一體同心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要得意忘形了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我來對付守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們從後方施放回復咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會受到攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是敵人的數量...！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷根！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽會把我們當做攻擊目標？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概他們被設定成與外面怪物不同的行動模式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣前衛和後衛的配置就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷根？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然還不是很清楚...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這次的攻略很重要對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在...已經不能算是遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法阻止守衛騎士的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷、雷根！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨、笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷根 夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃到外面去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗屬性魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自爆魔法？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這明明要承擔很高的死亡懲罰...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...真是個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風精靈部隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是貓妖的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍騎士隊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉唷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了籌集裝備花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞麗莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噴火攻擊準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(260,425)}Braze
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風精靈隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附加攻擊準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(285,425)}Extra Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Fire Braze
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狂狼風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(321,423)}Fenrir Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還欠了那位守衛精靈很大的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且完成攻略的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都靠他給的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員突擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別退縮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓制住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小直！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身後就拜託妳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟隨他們倆人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員掉頭 撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論飛到何處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛到天空的盡頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛到世界的核心！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門不是因為任務參數才打不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(342,425)}Quest Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要使用系統管理者權限才能打開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩家是絕對打不開這扇門的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個應該是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 快用這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在轉移登入碼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始傳送了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 抓住我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 鍍金的勇者
